Package com.totalcross.knowcode.parse

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    NodeSax
    NodeSax access the nodes and attributes of the XML file.
    XmlContainerConstraintLayout
    XmlContainerConstraintLayout is responsible to parse a ConstraintLayout Android XML to a Container Totalcross.
    XmlContainerFactory
    XmlContainerFactory is responsible to read the XML file, verify what kind of view group is the layout and to instantiate the specialized class of XmlContainerLayout.
    XmlContainerFrameLayout
    XmlContainerFrameLayout is responsible to parse a FrameLayout Android XML to a Container Totalcross.
    XmlContainerLayout
    XmlContainerLayout is a super class that abstracts the common methods to specialized classes of layout.
    XmlContainerLinearLayout
    XmlContainerLinearLayout is responsible to parse a LinearLayout Android XML to a Container Totalcross.
    XmlContainerRelativeLayout
    XmlContainerRelativeLayout is responsible to parse a RelativeLayout Android XML to a Container Totalcross.
